
GT is 2D top-view tile-map mobile-friendly RPG rendering library using
JavaScript and HTML Canvas. It was extracted from my game Ghosttown with
goal to be smaller, simpler, more portable with fixed player character
in center and smoothly moving background.

Author

    Dusan Halicky <dusan.halicky@gmail.com>

